Seeing that thier smoke screen worked they headed back to the Predacon 
base.

On arriving Quickstrike dumped Waspinator's head in the CR Tank for 
repairs.  Inferno and Quickstrike then headed to the command room to 
meet with Hydras.
"Royalty!  On our route we encountered enemy soldiers." Inferno 
started to explain.
